overview:
Nathan Rodgers is the founder of GetItWithMe - an online resource and meeting place helping people to share in the purchase of items. GetItWithMe was started in 2008 after he realized there was a need for people to live a lifestyle they wanted without the need to commit all their resource.

Nathan started young in the information technology industry (at the age of 12, working at his parentâ€™s computer store). He studied business and information science in Queensland, Australia before moving to London, UK to pursue other interests.

From 1998 to 2000, while in Australia, he founded an online venture that reviewed and recommended restaurants, events, arts and sport to consumers throughout the east coast of Australia (Brisbane, Sydney), raising $1.5 million.
